@AwyeeDeaterBob I agree it’s not great but neither was first few gens of iPhones. I think it’ll only get better. The lenses will get better &amp; so will the heat/weight of the headgear.

Biggest leap imo was going wireless (that first Oculus w/ cords was bad).

I wish there was more competition tbh

@BradHuston Big institutions who follow CPI print aren’t the ones buying #BTC right now, so it makes sense why we don’t see a clear connection.

As adoption continues to grow &amp; bigger players get involved, I’d imagine the correlation/connection will only grow stronger.

Give it a few years

